    "description": "<p><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">You attempt to Charm a creature within range. Choose a Non-Hostile creature that can see and hear you.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">Make a <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Spell Check </strong>contested by the target’s <strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Charisma Save</strong>.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track);\">Success:</strong> The creature is <strong>Charmed</strong> by you for the duration or until it takes damage.</span></p><p style=\"box-sizing: border-box; user-select: text; scrollbar-width: thin; scrollbar-color: var(--color-scrollbar) var(--color-scrollbar-track); margin: 0.5em 0px; color: rgb(25, 24, 19); font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; font-style: normal; font-variant-ligatures: normal; font-variant-caps: normal; font-weight: 400; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: 2; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; widows: 2; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; white-space: normal; text-decoration-thickness: initial; text-decoration-style: initial; text-decoration-color: initial; text-align: start\"><span style=\"font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', 'Lucida Sans Unicode', 'Lucida Grande', 'Lucida Sans', Arial, sans-serif\">When the spell effect ends or you fail the Check, the creature realizes that you used magic to influence its mood and may become hostile towards you.</span></p><p></p><p><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\"><strong><span style=\"text-decoration: underline;\">Mana Point Enhancements</span></strong></span></p><ul><li><p><strong>Hostile Charm: (1 MP)</strong> Cast this on any creature.</p></li><li><p><strong>Clear Suspicion: (2 MP)</strong> Target will no longer realize that magic has been cast on them.</p></li><li><p><strong>More Friends: (2 MP)</strong> Add an additional target to the effect of this spell and increase the range by 10 Spaces.</p></li><